title: GUCCI MANE, BIG BANK, DJ SCREAM - 6 GODS!!!!
itunes:title: GUCCI MANE, BIG BANK, DJ SCREAM - 6 GODS!!!!
description:
GUCCI MANE joins BIG BANK and DJ SCREAM on Big Facts for a classic episode. Gucci discusses "The New 1017", where Gucci stands with with several rappers, ZONE 6, his upcoming book, how prison changed him, the young rap generation, loyalty and more!
